      "description": "Presenting a remarkably well-maintained example that perfectly balances luxury and performance. This vehicle is finished in a sophisticated Deep Charcoal Metallic paint that retains a deep, mirror-like gloss, though a discerning eye will notice a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with responsible road use. The body panels are straight and free of significant dents or scratches. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary; the premium black leather upholstery has been regularly conditioned and shows no tears or heavy bolster wear. As a non-smoker vehicle, the interior smells fresh, and all high-tech amenities\u2014including the touchscreen navigation, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control\u2014are in perfect working order. Under the hood, the engine runs quietly and pulls strongly, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. Within the last 1,000 miles, it has received a full synthetic oil service and a fresh set of filters. The tires are matching name-brand units with approximately 75% tread remaining, ensuring a smooth and safe ride. This car is a turn-key opportunity for a buyer seeking a reliable, high-quality vehicle that has been treated with genuine pride of ownership.",
